msgctxt "9b16ffce-8c28-48f2-91c2-7463f9099fcc"
msgid ""
"To cure {g|Encyclopedia:AbilityDamage}ability damage{/g}, use a "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Spell}spell{/g} (or spell scroll), such as "
