msgctxt "5b3d695a-0ba1-4898-a44d-093f43903c26"
msgid ""
"Your enemy {t|TargetUnit} is highly resistant to "
"{g|Encyclopedia:Energy_Damage}energy damage{/g} with the descriptor "
"{t|Descriptor}."
