"an obstacle, picking a lock on a door or a chest, disarming a trap, moving "
"something heavy, reading an inscription in an ancient language, and many "
"others.\n"
"Different tasks require different skills. If you have several characters "
"selected at the same time, the {g|Encyclopedia:CA_Types}action{/g} will be "
"performed by the character with the highest skill bonus, so you should "
"select the whole party before attempting a check."
msgstr ""
